         </div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
               <p>O Lord, help.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary" xml:lang="ru">
            <p> Относительно формулы см. <ref type="introduction">IV.3.E.a</ref>. Форма беты близка <ref type="inscription">V 46</ref> и <ref type="inscription">V 50</ref>.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary" xml:lang="en">
            <p>On the formula, see <ref type="introduction">IV.3.E.a</ref>. The shape of beta is similar to <ref type="inscription">V 46</ref> and <ref type="inscription">V 50</ref>.</p>
         </div>
